<h2 class='page-intro'>CES Exhibitor News Conference Opportunities </h2>
<p class="intro">All media day events and CES news conferences, unless otherwise requested, will be included in the official CES Media Events Schedule and distributed on site at CES.</p>  

<h3 style="margin-bottom: -5px;"><img alt="CES Media Day" src="/CES/media/exhibitor-images/exhibitor-media-day_505x233.jpg" style="float: right; margin: auto 10px;" />CES Media Days</h3>

<p><strong>Media Day 1:</strong> Noon-2:45 PM, Jan. 7, 2018<br />
<strong>Media Day 2:</strong> 8 AM-5:45 PM, Jan. 8, 2018<br />
<strong>Location:</strong> Mandalay Bay</p>

<p>Make your major product or company news announcement exclusively to registered CES media and industry analysts with a Media Day news conference before the show floor opens.</p>

<p><strong>Selection in August 2017</strong><br />
You should receive your Media Day selection number in an email in early July.</p>

<p>If you do not receive a Media Day selection number, you can apply to be on the waitlist for any open slots, which will be filled on a first-come, first-served basis.</p>

<p><a href="/Exhibitor/Media-and-PR-Opportunities/News-Conferences/Media-Day-Wait-List.aspx"><img alt="" src="/CES/media/logos-and-icons/MDtimeslotbutton_1.jpg" /></a></p>
